# 🧠 SAP Professionals

## 💼 Key Modules
- SAP FICO, MM, SD, PP, HCM, ABAP, BASIS

## 🧠 What Clients Value
- Deep functional knowledge in at least one module
- Experience with S/4HANA migrations or implementations
- Good communication with business stakeholders

## 📌 Interview Tips
- Know business processes inside-out
- Be ready to give examples of customizations, integrations, or rollouts
