# 📄 CV & Portfolio Tips

- Keep your resume under 2 pages
- Use bullet points with achievements (not just responsibilities)
- Link to GitHub or portfolio site
- Tailor your CV to the job (highlight relevant tech/tools)
🔹 resources/career-growth.md
